### ============================================================
### EMPLOYEE MANAGEMENT API — HTTP Client (Module 1-9)
### Dùng với IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client hoặc VS Code REST Client
###
### ⚠️  Từ Module 9: Mọi API (trừ /api/auth/**) đều cần JWT token
###    Bước 1: Chạy [M9-1] hoặc [M9-2] để lấy token
###    Bước 2: Copy token vào biến @adminToken / @userToken bên dưới
### ============================================================

### ── Khai báo biến token (paste token vào đây sau khi login) ──
@adminToken = paste_admin_token_here
@userToken  = paste_user_token_here
@baseUrl    = http://localhost:8080


### ============================================================
###  MODULE 9 — AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================================

### [M9-1] Đăng nhập ADMIN (default: admin/admin123)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### [M9-2] Đăng nhập USER (default: user/user123)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "user123"
}

###

### [M9-3] Đăng ký tài khoản mới (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newadmin",
  "password": "pass123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

###

### [M9-4] Đăng ký tài khoản mới (USER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "pass123",
  "role": "USER"
}

###

### [M9-5] Không có token → 403 Forbidden
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Accept: application/json

###

### [M9-6] Token sai → 403 Forbidden
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here
Accept: application/json

###

### [M9-7] USER thử tạo nhân viên → 403 Forbidden (chỉ ADMIN mới được)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "test user",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "position": "Dev",
  "salary": 10000000,
  "departmentId": 1
}

###

### ============================================================
###  MODULE 1 — HELLO
### ============================================================

### [1] Hello — kiểm tra server chạy
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hello
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
###  MODULE 3-4 — EMPLOYEES (cần ADMIN token cho write operations)
### ============================================================

### [2] Get ALL employees (USER hoặc ADMIN đều được)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Get employees — filter theo department
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees?department=Engineering
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Get employee by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [5] Search — tìm theo tên HOẶC phòng ban
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees/search?keyword=nguyen
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [6] Create employee mới (chỉ ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "hoang van em",
  "email": "em.hoang@company.com",
  "position": "DevOps Engineer",
  "salary": 28000000,
  "departmentId": 1
}

###

### [7] Update employee (chỉ ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/employees/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "salary": 35000000,
  "position": "Senior Backend Developer"
}

###

### [8] Delete employee (chỉ ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/employees/5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
###  MODULE 3-4 — DEPARTMENTS
### ============================================================

### [9] Get ALL departments (USER hoặc ADMIN đều được)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/departments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [10] Create department mới (chỉ ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/departments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Marketing",
  "description": "Marketing and communications"
}

###

### [11] Create department trùng tên → 400 Business Error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/departments
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Engineering",
  "description": "Trùng tên — sẽ báo lỗi"
}

###

### ============================================================
###  MODULE 8 — ACTUATOR & REPORTS
### ============================================================

### [12] Actuator — health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### [13] Actuator — app info
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/info
Accept: application/json

###

### [14] Actuator — JVM memory
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/metrics/jvm.memory.used
Accept: application/json

###

### [15] Report summary (Cache MISS lần đầu — xem log)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [16] Report summary (Cache HIT — gọi trong 60s, không thấy log)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [17] Report by department
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/by-department
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
###  MODULE 2 — UTILITIES
### ============================================================

### [18] Demo BCrypt hash
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/hash?password=mySecret123
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================================
###  ERROR CASES — Module 5 Validation & Exception Handling
### ============================================================

### [E1] Validation error — thiếu field bắt buộc → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### [E2] Not Found — ID không tồn tại → 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees/999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [E3] Search keyword quá ngắn → 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/employees/search?keyword=a
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [E4] Email trùng → 400 Business Error
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Duplicate",
  "email": "an.nguyen@company.com",
  "position": "Tester",
  "salary": 10000000,
  "departmentId": 1
}

###

### [E5] Login sai password → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### [E6] Register username đã tồn tại → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "pass123",
  "role": "USER"
}